snippet.title: Across Kiloparsecs - Gameplay Trailer - First Scene
snippet.description:
A quick view of gameplay for the upcoming visual novel game Across Kiloparsecs currently available to wishlist on Steam at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2505080/Across_Kiloparsecs/

Background music is "Borealis" by Bloodless Mushroom. This game features a full soundtrack of ambient music by Bloodless Mushroom.
